{"tid":1182891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港海灘飲品膠樽為患 內地品牌「怡寶」佔最多","createTime":"2019-06-02T13:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T15:52:18.000Z","uid":3090,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"291d00b17ba0fb82e1a04217bf25a2816bac596a","tid":1182891,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfanyVq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfanyVq.png&h=d6ac81cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8S0KNfr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8S0KNfr.png&h=a4d34c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n綠惜地球過去1年調查香港海灘膠樽垃圾，發現最常見是華潤集團旗下的內地品牌怡寶膠樽。綠惜地球提供圖片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bfzLwG9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbfzLwG9.png&h=cd4da805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n膠樽來源上，簡體及繁體字品牌各佔48%，餘下不到4%為其他語言。綠惜地球提供圖片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LKC7fB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LKC7fB.png&h=647718cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n綠惜地球認為，三面環海的香港灘岸深受內地垃圾影響，不容掉以輕心。綠惜地球提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n綠惜地球過去1年調查香港海灘膠樽垃圾，共收集11,321個飲品膠樽，發現最常見是華潤集團旗下的內地品牌怡寶膠樽，佔17.7%。其次是可樂系列和維他系列，分別佔16.6%和15.2%。三大品牌膠樽已佔香港海灘膠樽垃圾一半。<br />\n<br />\n膠樽來源上，簡體及繁體字品牌各佔48%，餘下不到4%為其他語言。綠惜地球認為，三面環海的香港灘岸深受內地垃圾影響，不容掉以輕心。<br />\n<br />\n綠惜地球指，中國是全球製造最多海洋塑膠垃圾的國家，要治本要四管齊下，包括盡早推出飲品及包裝容器的生產者責任法規；未立法前要求怡寶、康師傅等品牌訂定進取的減塑目標；加強廢物收集及回收的基礎建設；加強粵港政府合作，防堵廢塑料等生活垃圾落入河川和大海。<br />\n<br />\n本港飲品膠樽回收率長年低迷，2017年只有6.8%。綠惜地球促請環保署盡早完成膠樽生產者責任法規的顧問研究，提出立法對策。"},{"pid":"adabc2eb75a34bbe61b8b08e384c3e6f901f51e3","tid":1182891,"uid":58038,"like":31,"dislike":9,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:39:54.000Z","msg":"嘩<br />\n咁撚大枝塞落龜龜個鼻到<br />\n有冇環保撚發表兩句?"},{"pid":"cfc3107e82c1ebaa23025274d982b848bbd59e56","tid":1182891,"uid":85574,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:43:04.000Z","msg":"咁都唔撚係大陸漂過嚟/旅行團搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港大部分地方都無怡寶水賣"},{"pid":"74e45769df63ccdb6993f23c3270a56f42f678d4","tid":1182891,"uid":54303,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:43:46.000Z","msg":"國家又送大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9181478ff20f90db36a6d67e119cc7f4a736a75f","tid":1182891,"uid":36478,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd0fc127500ca8ea029296f42e24c01ce3a5dbc","tid":1182891,"uid":33174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"adabc2eb75a34bbe61b8b08e384c3e6f901f51e3","tid":1182891,"uid":58038,"like":31,"dislike":9,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:39:54.000Z","msg":"嘩<br />\n咁撚大枝塞落龜龜個鼻到<br />\n有冇環保撚發表兩句?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:50:47.000Z","msg":"咁大枝點撚樣塞啊？<br />\n塞唔到姐係冇事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14eaa4c4a6fd9ef3a2ddbe39db84704076200c2","tid":1182891,"uid":8897,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:59:39.000Z","msg":"香港人好少買怡寶水 應該係d內地旅行團帶黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa191ee21ad702cfa027d534ca07d11f7e346b45","tid":1182891,"uid":12591,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"tvb只會報殘體字同正體字各佔一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0283f003f724af4e048b8695f39a7eb9424f549b","tid":1182891,"uid":126054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"中央又送大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要不是中央,香港................"},{"pid":"4067e3031a5b7f38eabbb5409d5b208b7bf9efc9","tid":1182891,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"等環保撚塞到入龜鼻我地咪唔買樽裝囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66d44fcc0c0fe6ed33f24ab74275a57fc64ce8f","tid":1182891,"uid":42629,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:18:29.000Z","msg":"就算第五位康師傅主要都係大陸有得買。<br />\n基本上可以肯定大部份膠樽都係支那人掉（包括香港品牌嘅樽）"},{"pid":"8bb4b472c3c5818d24d2b6db87573e96cc87986e","tid":1182891,"uid":28435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:27:10.000Z","msg":"屠殺支那人=環保"},{"pid":"a8775a9112e86252e619e68ac8cbc74befcccce1","tid":1182891,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:28:26.000Z","msg":"好執唔執膠樽做研究<br />\n<br />\n佢地都好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nd樽唔係多數飲完水用黎裝尿既咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8f341a46b7eb897572fda9d7e35a7a515bcdd9","tid":1182891,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:38:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a9e51b0ae4d712555872c887f5c93fb42c323ea5","tid":1182891,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"環保回應下"},{"pid":"2f673634514335190aea17c4da06579910241707","tid":1182891,"uid":242866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"支那真係無嘢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d66d53a04d9ae08973378169d53a570fabcae6","tid":1182891,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9e51b0ae4d712555872c887f5c93fb42c323ea5","tid":1182891,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"環保回應下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"